{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01CgjN7bMz3g9uhNdvnq6hHB","type":"tool_result","content":"# Askewly Design System Index\n\n## Primary Entry Point\n- **Entry Protocol**: https://ui.askewly.com/llms/docs/design-system/entry-protocol.md\n  - \"Start here: what to fetch, in what order, per design task type (new screen / improving existing UI / single component)\"\n\n## Core Documentation\n- **Principles**: https://ui.askewly.com/llms/docs/design-system/principles.md\n- **Anti-patterns**: https://ui.askewly.com/llms/docs/design-system/anti-patterns.md\n- **Style Signature**: https://ui.askewly.com/llms/docs/design-system/style-signature.md\n\n## Tokens & Taxonomy\n- **Token Source (JSON)**: https://ui.askewly.com/llms/tokens/askewly.tokens.json\n- **CSS Variables**: https://ui.askewly.com/llms/tokens/tokens.css\n- **Pattern Taxonomy**: https://ui.askewly.com/llms/docs/design-system/pattern-taxonomy.md\n- **Groups Reference**: https://ui.askewly.com/llms/docs/ui-vocabulary/groups.yml\n\n## Contracts & Models\n- **Recipe Format**: https://ui.askewly.com/llms/docs/design-system/recipe-format.md\n- **Agent Asset Model**: https://ui.askewly.com/llms/docs/design-system/agent-asset-model.md\n- **Component Restyle**: https://ui.askewly.com/llms/docs/design-system/component-restyle.md\n- **Absorption Criteria**: https://ui.askewly.com/llms/docs/design-system/absorption-criteria.md\n\n## Knowledge\n- **Expressive Stack**: https://ui.askewly.com/llms/knowledge/expressive-stack.md\n\n## 42 Component Recipes\nOrganized by surface: application-ui (6), commerce (6), data-display (8), docs (4), feedback (2), forms (4), layout (2), marketing (5), navigation (5), overlays (4)."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"05f608d7-b1fc-4ad3-a101-9110f925f986","uuid":"f59fdfa9-222c-488c-9742-d49cadc9eb93","timestamp":"2026-07-18T12:31:23.140Z","tool_use_result":{"bytes":12294,"code":200,"codeText":"OK","result":"# Askewly Design System Index\n\n## Pri